Installing flask-galatea_file
=============================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Python 2.7 or later (http://www.python.org/)
 * trytond (http://www.tryton.org/)
 * trytond-galatea

Installation
------------

Once you've downloaded and unpacked the flask-galatea source release,
copy galatea directory in main flask app.

Edit your App flask and register a new blueprint:

from galatea import galatea
app.register_blueprint(galatea, url_prefix='/<lang>')
